Step 1 : Open terminal by pressing Ctrl + Alt + T
Strp 2 : Adding the repository 
         sudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/atom
         Press ENTER if asks for permission
Step 3 : Update the Repository
         Sudo apt-get update
Step 4 : Install Atom
         sudo apt-get install atom
Step 5 : Search Atom in Apllication window and click on Atom 

Heeeeyy,Great Mate you have successfully installed Atom in Your Machine.
